title: Updating Old Maps for a Fresh Gaming Experience
description: Join us in this devlog as we update old maps for a fresh gaming experience on Roblox! Get a behind-the-scenes look at the process of revamping uncopylocked games

title: Inside Look: Creating a Roblox Game from Scratch
description: Get an inside look at the process of creating a Roblox game from scratch in this devlog. From vision to Roblox Studio to scripting tutorial, see how game development comes to life on Roblox!
